metadata.description: Featuring 6 characters, totaling 6,669 tokens, ZombyWorld is a story, music and visual universe, building a Comic Book, TV series, game and Soundtrack with input from the community through a writers room and music studio for holders with top filmmakers, musicians and artists brought in for chats with the community. Building ultimately to an entirely new world, into a series, and launching OtherWorld Comics which will allow creators to create and publish new projects like a real life comic book store, and as a creative collaborative space.
metadata.name: ZombyWorld #1
